{"type": "article", "id": 61504, "title": "一波奥斯卡广告发布，Urban Decay 将推出“权力的游戏”系列彩妆 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-02-25T05:57:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1040, "name": "奥斯卡"}, {"id": 1203, "name": "权力的游戏"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190225123414zJD7fyn6SktoPjAK.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"VqCE\"><b><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BuMc1YFFCAS/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zendaya</a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BuMc1YFFCAS/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Coleman 成为兰蔻最新全球形象代言人。</a></b>她曾出演电影《蜘蛛侠：英雄归来》中的米歇尔·“MJ”·琼斯一角，还曾获得 Billboard 和 Hollywoodlife 的最佳着装前三名。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123439Vl3oYGOHTWJAM04d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123439a5ClzGAKIFfHLohS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"CW7e\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BuLTU4zhJQu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Urban Decay 宣布将推出《冰与火之歌：权力的游戏》系列彩妆，</b></a>预计在四月份面世。目前还不确定具体包括哪些产品，不过根据发布的图片推测，应该是和剧中角色相关的眼妆产品。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123510yLgzujh9f3KDY6I2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123510hkqVHBSK4OGMJ5pW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"A7ap\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1855335174/4342803671008556\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>江浙沪地区连绵的阴雨天气，淘宝顺势推出“种太阳 ”活动。</b></a>用户在淘宝输入“种太阳，就能在手机屏幕上看到淘宝制造的太阳，还会提示用户是“第 XXX 位种太阳小能手”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251235382NvLpt37E5JOCjA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.792000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123537fScuJwaWx6Zy2G97.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.710667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"Gd4K\"><a href=\"https://vans.com.cn/article/comfycush-sh-event?utm_source=pc_homepage&amp;utm_medium=pc_banner1&amp;utm_campaign=ownsite\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Vans 将举行沉浸式互动体验 “ComfyCush High” 上海站活动，主题为重返高中时代。</b></a>活动是为了品牌的 ComfyCush 技术面世，新技术将提高鞋款的舒适度，将于 3 月 2 日 和 3 月 3 日在上海民生现代美术馆开启。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123603m2J6ptaQrhegF4nL.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.606440\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123603pLZHKcYFABokqx32.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663685\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123603o8iZ7aLmHlfs390M.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.932021\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p line=\"SUom\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u75uo3dfvgw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>凌仕发布了三支 ASMR 广告，</b></a>详细展示了男士在浴室如何使用它的产品剔除体毛。（完整视频点击链接观看）</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225123619OCtb68Bih7jEcrsV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562893\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"uK9J\">今天第 91 届奥斯卡金像奖颁奖礼已经结束，广告商们的作品也发布了。</p><p line=\"KazV\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/whpJ19RJ4JY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>耐克的 <em>Dream Crazier </em>展现了一些顶尖女性运动员的“疯狂”时刻，</b></a>强调赋予女性平等的权利，也减少更多的性别偏见。值得一提的是，画外音由小威讲述。创意代理商来自 W+K 波兰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x0841yb7pwb\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124059RHZdiLWyk1fGKUOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124059olByFSk8xqCOV7Pj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124100Q1exKEAIdvnJ7ZrV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124059iJcLZ1leVDCvpmIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251240597uxtKBhH2vfQ6SqI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124059hiuLcm82bEYtwJ6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124100J7ztB9onq40ClgbQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124100mA3RiwhE1OJeDW6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124100hDNiXZjzpYIJry5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124101UVFXOgKfQan5jmDR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124101uvZn9ctVS60rRiyH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124101KJlfGym0nuMIZxPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124101RXbeSrfoyEDLm5VZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124101iHqvFNcfuEklB69n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251241017FAZdrPMIkj5yi6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"jfHP\"><b><a href=\"https://youtu.be/TcsT9Vlznz8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21 世纪福克斯的短片宣传了讲述皇后乐队的歌舞传记电影《波西米亚狂想曲：摇滚传说》</a>。</b>皇后乐队的粉丝在收到电影的蓝光碟片后，化身 Freddie Mercury 在家中舞动起来。创意代理商是 Ralph。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0841kmwfik\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><p line=\"1RMa\"><a href=\"https://www.shutterstock.com/blog/2019-oscar-pop-movie-posters?utm_medium=Affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=admitad%20Shutterstock&amp;utm_term=205380&amp;utm_source=274393&amp;irgwc=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Shutterstock 发布了第七届奥斯卡海报系列，</b></a>从著名波普艺术家们的标志性作品中汲取灵感，为奥斯卡今年提名的最佳电影设计了风格迥异鲜明的海报。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124505tgpTc2PYQim4lnWF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.336653\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自 Richard Hamilton</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124451fce5sQoqdzwH3N0R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.339321\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自 Daniel Danger</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124313xDjaoib78AqkngtK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.339960\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自 Kehinde Wiley</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124313SH7RYwqjtEcpozMg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.337972\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自&nbsp;Andy Warhol</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124314FHPGA3E2uVhd1Uge.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.246548\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自&nbsp;Tony Fitzpatrick</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124313nCPv5xKhf6XGHQgo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.521253\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自 Jack Kirby</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124526MVRPKwsYO7N248HL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334653\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自 Roy Lichtenstein</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124313b7kOxyJfQFIYHT2V.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.340637\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\"> <figcaption class=\"\">灵感来自&nbsp;Sister Mary Corita Kent</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p line=\"u2QH\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/-czP8snXuMU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>百威旗下的啤酒品牌米凯罗 Pure Gold <em>Call From Nature </em>强调自然的概念。</b></a>城市中的人们逃离都市，回归原始人在大自然中享受低卡啤酒。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0841r1952m\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"nhYB\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/aJaSCqPvwOA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 的奥斯卡广告 <em>#HeyGoogle, Let's Go To The Movies </em>为 Google Home Mini、Pixel 3 XL 等打广告。</b></a>片中混剪了各种电影片段，比如《2001太空漫游》和《伯德小姐》，还为 Google 产品安排了几个角色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e0841whdgi7\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"nhYB\" class=\"\">题图来自：Nike YouTube 截图</p>"}